sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant B as Billing Service
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant O as Outbox Publisher
    participant K as Kafka
    participant A as Ads Service
    participant N as Notification Service

    U->>G: POST /api/v1/ads/{adId}/promotions + Idempotency-Key
    G->>B: purchase promotion
    B->>P: BEGIN
    B->>P: INSERT payment + promotion(pending_publication)
    B->>P: INSERT outbox event promotion.paid
    B->>P: COMMIT
    B-->>G: 201 accepted
    G-->>U: payment accepted

    O->>P: poll outbox
    O->>K: publish promotion.paid
    A->>K: publish ad.published
    K->>B: consume ad.published
    B->>P: activate promotion (starts_at/expires_at)
    B->>K: publish promotion.activated
    K->>N: consume promotion.activated
    N-->>U: email/push notification
